 <purpose>
   <p>
     The Document and version identification application module supports
     the requirement to identify and version documents.  
   </p>
 </purpose>

 <inscope>
  <li>
    The identification of documents which includes an identifying label or
    number, an organization or person in organization which assigned the
    label or number;
  </li>

  <li>the identification of versions for documents (which can be null);</li>
  
  <li>a data structure for specifying document categories.</li>
 </inscope>



 <definition>
   <term id="document">document</term>
   <def>
     Information and its support medium. 
 
     <example>
       A drawing, a test report, an ISO standard are examples of document.
     </example>

     <note>
       The medium may be paper, photograph, digital files, optical computer
       disc, magnetic, electronic storage, or a combination thereof. 
     </note>
</def>
 </definition>

